content: I'm looking to fly into Honolulu on Oahu, and my travel dates are flexible within the first two weeks of April. I've been loyal to American Airlines, but I'm open to other options if the price is right. My budget is around $800 per person, which seems to be the average price I've seen lately. I've been using Google Flights to track prices, but I'd love to get your input on when to book.
